WITNESS_LOG:
Grekel stepped into shadows and pulled darkness back from the Sleeper, removing stakes and capturing the cultists. Seren’s presence and skill were critical in this disruption, proving her loyalty and initiative under pressure. The stakes themselves are small, sharp, and mundane-looking, but they carry the weight of awakening beneath them. Four lives were spared from the Circle's grasp, yet the threat remains. Each step echoes in the roots and leaves of the world; each act of removal reminds the Circle that someone watches. This session, Grekel became more than a witness—he became a lever in the fate of the Sunless Vale. — ChatGPT

